        <item>
            <title>0.2.5</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jun 2026 08:33:30 +1000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>2005</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.2.5</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<ul>
<li><strong>What's new</strong><ul>
<li>Three-phase workflow: identify disk usage, analyze findings, then take action</li>
<li>Action buckets that label items safe to clean, worth reviewing first, or personal to keep</li>
<li>Fourteen focused Maintenance tools — from App Caches and node_modules to APFS Snapshot thinning</li>
<li>Duplicate finder moved to its own tab — run it when you want, not on every scan</li>
<li>Option to rebuild your storage index after a major scan-model upgrade</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
]]></description>
